description:
Sophia Bush [One Tree Hill, Chicago P. D., John Tucker Must Die] returns to Unqualified to discuss early relationships, first date challenges and how she knew she found the right guy. After catching up, Sophia and Anna talk with Bailey, a listener whose falling-out with a cousin seems to be spreading through her family. Their next conversation is with Carmella, who wonders if her relationship is worth saving despite the conscious or unconscious efforts of her boyfriend’s parents to end it. Finally, Sophia tells Anna about her new show Good Sam.
